Uses of Package
eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.enums

  • Packages that use eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.enums 
    Package Description
    eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.commands
    Contains the different types of commands used in and by JDroidLib.
    eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.device
    Contains classes used with and by JDroidLib to represent devices, their components and utilities that don't make sense in any other package.
    eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.enums
    Contains enumerations for use in the library.
    eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.interfaces
    Contains interfaces used internally by the JDroidLib library.
    eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.util
    Contains utility objects used for and by JDroidLibv2.
